OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FThe HMS Dragon has been deployed from
OL,7,FPortsmouth Naval Base for the Eastern
OL,8,FMediterranean to help protect Cyprus
OL,9,Fand RAF bases there from further
OL,10,Fattacks by Iran and its proxies.
OL,12,FOn March 2, an Iranian drone attack
OL,13,Ftargeted RAF Akrotiri, leading to the
OL,14,FPrime Minister announcing the ship's
OL,15,Fdeployment a day later.
OL,17,FCritics have accused the government of
OL,18,Fbeing slow to act, not only in the
OL,19,Fspeed at which they deployed the HMS
OL,20,FDragon but also in the time it has
OL,21,Ftaken the vessel to leave port.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
