OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FDefence Secretary John Healey said
OL,7,FBritish forces had been "working
OL,8,Ftirelessly, some 22 hours a day" to
OL,9,Fprepare the Type 45 destroyer, which
OL,10,Fwill join other US air defence
OL,11,Fdestroyers.
OL,13,FBut what is HMS Dragon, and what are
OL,14,Fits capabilities?
OL,16,FWhat is it?
OL,18,FHMS Dragon is one of the most advanced
OL,19,Fwarships in the world, according to
OL,20,Fthe Royal Navy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
