OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773216518
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FIt is one of six Type 45 air defence
OL,7,Fdestroyers, known as the Daring class,
OL,8,Fwhich were purpose-built for anti-
OL,9,Faircraft and anti-missile warfare.
OL,11,FInstantly recognisable by the large
OL,12,Fred Welsh Dragon on its bow, HMS
OL,13,FDragon is manned by more than 200
OL,14,Fpersonnel and is currently based in
OL,15,FPortsmouth.
OL,17,FDespite the name 'destroyer', the ship
OL,18,Fis built for a range of missions from
OL,19,Fcombating pirates and defending
OL,20,Fagainst air attacks, to delivering
OL,21,Fhumanitarian aid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
