OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773216518
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FWhat capabilities does it have?
OL,8,FAll six of the UK's Type 45 destroyers
OL,9,Ffeature a missile system known as Sea
OL,10,FViper, which is "designed to track,
OL,11,Ftarget and destroy a variety of high-
OL,12,Flevel air threats", including cruise
OL,13,Fmissiles, fighter jets and drones.
OL,15,FAccording to the Royal Navy, it can
OL,16,Flaunch eight missiles in under ten
OL,17,Fseconds and simultaneously guide up to
OL,18,F16, hitting targets with precision
OL,19,Ffrom over 70 miles away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
