PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773216518
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FIts multifunctional radar can detect
OL,7,Fair and surface targets from a
OL,8,Fdistance of 250 miles and is capable
OL,9,Fof tracking hundreds of targets
OL,10,Fsimultaneously.
OL,12,FAs well as two Phalanx 20mm close-in
OL,13,Fweapons systems, the ships have an
OL,14,Farray of weaponry, including the BAE
OL,15,FSystems 4.5-inch Mark 8 Mode 1, two
OL,16,F30mm DSM Mark 2s, two 7.62mm miniguns
OL,17,Fand up to six FN MAG general purpose
OL,18,Fmachine guns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
