PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773216518
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FThe Type 45 destroyers also feature a
OL,7,Fflight deck and hangar to support the
OL,8,Foperation of a single Merlin
OL,9,Fhelicopter, which can be used for
OL,10,F"round-the-clock maritime patrol",
OL,11,Foffensive attacks and search and
OL,12,Frescue missions.
OL,14,FWhat conflicts has the HMS Dragon been
OL,15,Finvolved in?
OL,17,FThe HMS Dragon's history goes all the
OL,18,Fway back to 1647, when the First
OL,19,FDragon was built in Chatham as a 38-
OL,20,Fgun fourth rate frigate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
