PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773216518
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FThe ship is now in its tenth
OL,7,Fiteration, launching in November 2008
OL,8,Fand beginning its first mission in
OL,9,FApril 2012.
OL,11,FPrevious incarnations of the ship took
OL,12,Fpart in the Seige of Havana in 1762 as
OL,13,Fpart of the Seven Years War, was
OL,14,Femployed in the suppression of the
OL,15,Fslave trade in the late 1800s and took
OL,16,Fpart in operations against German U-
OL,17,Fboats in the Second World War.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
